    <h1>Travel to Kyrgyzstan!</h1>

    <h2>Why visit?</h2>
    <p>
        Kyrgyzstan is a stunning country in Central Asia with breathtaking mountains, 
        crystal-clear lakes, and rich nomadic culture. One of the most famous destinations is 
        <span class="highlight">Lake Issyk-Kul</span>, the world's second-largest saline lake.
    </p>

    <h2>Top sights</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><span class="highlight">Issyk-Kul Lake</span> – relax on the beaches and enjoy the mountains.</li>
        <li>Alay Valley – hike and explore nature.</li>
        <li>Burana Tower – step back into history.</li>
        <li>Ala Archa National Park – perfect for trekking.</li>
    </ul>

